quran[22]{c,v,t}:
  11,108,"Sano aŵala ŵatachiŵa ŵambone nikuti tachiŵa mu Litimbe lya ku Mbepo, tachilonjela mwalakwemo mugachilonjelela mawunde ni mataka, ikaŵeje mutachisachila Ambuje ŵenu; (walakweo ni) ntuka wangamala"
  11,109,"Basi mmwe nkaŵa mu kaichila pa yaakuigalagatila ŵanganyao (yanti nganijiŵa milungu jakuona), ngaakugalagatila ikaŵeje mpela yaŵatiji pagalagatila achatatiŵao kala, soni chisimu Uwwe chitwalipile liunjili lyao mwakwana mwangali kupungusya"
  11,110,"Soni chisimu chene Musa twampele chitabu, basi ni wapatikene mwalakwemo ukangani, mwanti likaŵaga liloŵe lyalyalongolele lyakuumila kwa Ambuje ŵenu (lyangapa ilagasyo yekulungwa nnope ikaŵeje ku Kiyama) chisimu kungajilanyidwe chilikati chao, soni ŵanganyao ali nchikaiko chekulungwa chakuchikaichila chalakwecho"
  11,111,"Soni chisimu Ambuje ŵenu tachalipila ŵaliose mwa ŵanganyao masengo gao mwakwana, chisimu Jwalakwe abali syosope sya yaakutenda aŵele Jwasimanya chenene"
  11,112,"Basi lungamikani (mmwe Muhammadi ﷺ) yantite pakulamulidwa pamo ni aŵala ŵaatesile toba nomwe, soni jenumanja nkasumba mpika. Chisimu Jwalakwe ichindu yankutenda juŵele Jwakuilolechesya"
  11,113,"Ningasimpendechela kwa aŵala ŵaalitesile lupuso utakwika mwaunkwayiye Moto, kutendaga jenumanja n’di nganinkola akun’gosa jwangaŵaga Allah, kaneko jenumanja ningakulupusyidwa"
  11,114,"Soni jimikani Swala mwakolosya songa siŵili syamuusi (kundawi ni kwigulo), kwisa soni ndema sine syachilo, chisimu yambone ikutyosyaga yakusakala, chele nichikumbusyo kwa ŵakumbuchila"
  11,115,"Soni pililani, chisimutu Allah jwangajonanga malipilo ga ŵakolosya"
  11,116,"Anauli nganapatikana m’mikutula jaŵakala ŵenu achinsyene sigasiga syalunda, ŵakanya kuwatanganya pa chilambo, ikaŵeje ŵannonope mwa aŵala ŵatwajokwele mu ŵanganyao? Sano aŵala ŵaŵalitesile lupuso ŵajendelechele mu (yasambi) yaŵaliji nkusengwa nayo, niŵaliji ŵakuleŵa"
  11,117,"Sano Ambuje ŵenu nganaŵa ŵanti nikujijonanga misi mwalupuso, kutendaga achinsyene misijo ali ŵakutenda yambone"
  11,118,"Soni Ambuje ŵenu angasache angatesile achinaŵandu kuŵa nkutula umpepe (wakuya Usilamu), nambo ngaaleka kuŵa ali nkutindana"
  11,119,"Ikaŵeje ŵaŵatendele chanasa Ambuje ŵenu, sano kwaligongo lyele (lya chanasacho) ŵagumbile, soni maloŵe ga Ambuje ŵenu gamasile pagakwanilisyidwe (yanti): “Chisimu tinjijigumbasya Jahannama ni achimajini kwisa soni achinaŵandu wosopeŵene (ŵaŵaliji ŵakusakasya).”"
  11,120,"Sano yosope yatukunsimbila (mmwe Muhammadi ﷺ) mu abali sya Achimitenga ili yanti tun’dimbikasye nayo ntima wenu, sano mu aji (Sura ja Qur’aniji) im’bichilile yakuona, chamuko kwisa soni chikumbusyo ku ŵakulupilila"
  11,121,"Sano jilani kwa aŵala ŵangakukulupilila: “Panganyani (masengo genu) mwachimpanganyichisye, nombe uwwe tupanganye (mwatupanganyichisye).”"
  11,122,"“Soni jembecheyani, nombe uwwe tukwembecheya.”"
  11,123,"Soni Allah ni Nsyene yakusisika ya kumawunde ni petaka, soni Kukwakwe nikwakuujila ichindu yosope, basi mun’galagatilani ni kwegamila Kukwakwe, sano Ambuje ŵenu nganaŵa ŵanti ningaimanya yankutenda ŵanganyammwe"
  12,1,Alif-Lâm-Râ. Aga ni ma Ȃya ga m’Chitabu chakusalichisya
  12,2,Chisimu Uwwe tujitulwisye jalakwejo kuŵa Qur’an jacharabu kuti jenumanja mpate kumanyilila
  12,3,"Uwwe tukunsimulila (mmwe Muhammadi ﷺ) abali syambone nnope pakun’juwulila aji Qur’an, ni mwaliji ŵangachimanya chilichose (chakwayana ni Qur’anijo) nkanijiŵe (kuntuluchila)"
  12,4,"(Kumbuchilani) katema kajwaŵechete Yusufu kwababagwe kuti: “E baba ŵangu! Chisimu une nasiweni kulugono ndondwa likumi kwisa jimo, lyuŵa ni mwesi, naiweni yosopeyo inankusujudila une.”"
  12,5,"Jwalakwe jwatite: “E mwanangu! Nkaasagamukulila sagamisi syenusyo achakuluŵenu, atakwisa mwantendele malindi, chisimu shetani kwa mundu aŵele mmagongo jwakuonechela.”"
  12,6,"“Soni iyyoyopeyo Ambuje ŵenu tachinsagula nikun’jiganya gopolela sagamisi, nikwanilisya ukoto Wakwe kukwenu kwisa soni kwiŵasa lya Yaakubu, mpela yaŵatite pakuukwanilisya kalakala kwa achatatiŵenu ŵaŵili Ibrahima ni Isihaka, chisimu Ambuje ŵenu ni Ŵakumanyilila nnope, Ŵalunda lwakusokoka.”"